                                        A discount for tourist groups, publication of promotional content. You can book a promo-round to test out buses.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="span6">
                    <h2 class="with-border">feedback:</h2>
                    <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide section">
                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                            <div class="active item">
